Step 1: Place Devices in Packet Tracer
- 1 × Router
- 1 × Switch
- 6 × PCs
- 1 × Server

Step 2: Connect Devices
- Router G0/0 → Switch F0/1 (trunk link).
- IT PCs → Switch F0/2–3.
- Admin PCs → Switch F0/4–5.
- Student PCs → Switch F0/6–7.
- Server → Switch F0/8.

Step 3: Create VLANs on the Switch
- Click Switch → CLI tab.
- Enter VLAN configuration (check VLAN configuration for code)

Step 4: Assign Switch Ports to VLANs
